{"tid":1496903,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"集思廣益點樣應對香港文革式批鬥","createTime":"2019-08-22T17:14:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-22T17:36:39.000Z","uid":47617,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"eef656616046f96eacdc4ce5e14784625a9dd1b3","tid":1496903,"uid":47617,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T17:14:20.000Z","msg":"睇到國泰員工因敢言被炒<br />\n睇到將執業律師因敢言要求解釋<br />\n睇到民建聯張國均帶頭要求藍絲家長篤灰投訴<br />\n<br />\n所有事香港人睇得清清楚楚 白色恐怖 文革批鬥 打壓立場唔同既人 作為受過教育既人 可以點樣應對<br />\n<br />\n集思廣益！"},{"pid":"09118ba5e4e852530119b2c34a9239c4ce496b93","tid":1496903,"uid":47617,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T17:14:26.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"cbeb48beae075b93487deb6db6e55a77c4a3f1f0","tid":1496903,"uid":47617,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T17:14:39.000Z","msg":"集思廣益"},{"pid":"89b9226feb554ea40f86bbdad6d0b8ac1b501a4b","tid":1496903,"uid":12179,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T17:15:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab4fe19d25de03e2e4694c2a5b01965637100c71","tid":1496903,"uid":47617,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T17:15:13.000Z","msg":"有冇乜野對策"},{"pid":"fe0e0e8fa7e110fb34a78a75176f0c41e09b3ff8","tid":1496903,"uid":47617,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T17:15:44.000Z","msg":"集思廣益"},{"pid":"4af7fc4cfb6039679177addac88937097f4c7813","tid":1496903,"uid":263448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T17:16:45.000Z","msg":"開公司請番晒"},{"pid":"465fdeb3e52467a8ed6d399d9fec799acc02f3aa","tid":1496903,"uid":49336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T17:18:14.000Z","msg":"唔好返工 消費減到最低<br />\n做人無欲無求 冇人騷擾到你"},{"pid":"1c840191aef5811eb156a688f0ef946573eb14d3","tid":1496903,"uid":54125,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T17:27:51.000Z","msg":"國泰呢單其實唔係淨係關香港事<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好多外國人都會搭<br />\n佢咁樣亂搞會嚴重影響機組人員<br />\n不論示氣同集中力都有問題<br />\n而且仲用中國空域嚟做威脅<br />\n一陣佢唔高興打你一隻機落嚟都唔係無可能架喎<br />\n<br />\n所以呢單好需要要搞佢推出國際<br />\n講Chinazi嘅魔掌已經伸到出嚟<br />\n希望國際制裁中國嘅航空公司<br />\n唔畀佢哋飛外國領空，除非佢放棄國泰控制權"},{"pid":"96ee36d5404741448b9bbad82af86946857a7c81","tid":1496903,"uid":47617,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T17:36:39.000Z","msg":"其實睇到未來會開始左一系列既清算 學校文革批鬥篤灰 藍絲做緊既野已經係無道德可言"}]}